Description: USB Device Monitor - System Tray Application
 A lightweight system tray application that provides a GUI wrapper
 around the usb-devices command, making it easy to monitor USB
 devices in real-time with a user-friendly interface.
 .
 Features:
  * GUI wrapper for usb-devices command
  * Real-time USB device monitoring
  * System tray integration
  * Detailed device information display
  * Automatic detection of device changes
  * Cross-platform compatibility (Linux) 